---
interface Props {
  goal: number;
  deadline: Date;
}

const { goal, deadline } = Astro.props;
const deadlineIso = deadline.toISOString().slice(0, 10);
---

<aside class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-white/[0.02] p-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">
  <h3 class="mb-2 text-base font-semibold text-white">How this pre-order works</h3>
  <ol class="list-decimal space-y-2 pl-5 text-[var(--color-muted)]">
    <li>
      You pre-order today at the full launch price. Your card is charged now via Stripe.
    </li>
    <li>
      If we hit <span class="font-semibold text-white">{goal} pre-orders by {deadlineIso}</span>, we build it and email you the files within 21 days.
    </li>
    <li>
      If we don&rsquo;t hit the goal, every pre-order is refunded in full within 48 hours of the deadline. You lose nothing.
    </li>
  </ol>
  <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">
    We build what the market actually wants, instead of guessing. You only pay for things enough other people also wanted.
  </p>
</aside>
